    category: 'Home Office',
    readTime: '11',
  },
  {
    title: 'Ergonomic Chair Buying Guide: How to Choose the Right One for Your Body',
    excerpt: 'Stop back pain. Learn exactly what to look for in an ergonomic chair — lumbar support, seat depth, armrests, and the best models at every budget.',
    href: '/blog/ergonomic-chair-buying-guide/',
    date: '2026-07-14',
    category: 'Ergonomics',
    readTime: '10',
  },
  {
    title: 'Monitor Setup Guide: Single vs Dual vs Ultrawide for Productivity',
    excerpt: 'The science of screen real estate. Compare single, dual, and ultrawide monitor setups and find the best configuration for your workflow.',
    href: '/blog/monitor-setup-guide/',
    date: '2026-07-14',
    category: 'Tech & Gear',
    readTime: '9',
  },
  {
    title: '10 Small Space Home Office Ideas (That Actually Work)',
    excerpt: 'No spare room? No problem. Creative, practical home office setups for closets, corners, bedrooms, and shared spaces — all from real remote workers.',
    href: '/blog/small-space-home-office-ideas/',
    date: '2026-07-13',
    category: 'Home Office',
    readTime: '8',
  },
  {
    title: 'Standing Desk Guide: Manual vs Electric vs Converter — Which to Buy?',
    excerpt: 'Everything you need to know about standing desks. Compare manual crank, electric motor, and desktop converters across price, stability, and ease of use.',
    href: '/blog/standing-desk-guide/',
    date: '2026-07-13',
    category: 'Ergonomics',
    readTime: '10',
  },
  {
    title: 'Remote Work Productivity: 15 Science-Backed Tips to Stay Focused at Home',
    excerpt: 'Distractions, procrastination, and Zoom fatigue are real. These 15 research-backed strategies will help you stay focused and get more done — without burning out.',
    href: '/blog/remote-work-productivity-tips/',
    date: '2026-07-12',
    category: 'Productivity',
    readTime: '9',
  },
  {
    title: 'Best Webcams and Microphones for Remote Meetings in 2026',
    excerpt: 'Look and sound professional on every call. Compare the best webcams and microphones for remote workers at every budget — from $30 to $300.',
